{Speech 2}{}{This is private property, be a good fellow and move along.}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Who lives here?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Fine, I'll go.}
{Speech 3}{}{This is the Vestin Ranch, home of Councilman Vestin.}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{I need to see the councilman, please.}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{All right. I'm leaving.}
{Speech 4}{}{He's very busy right now.}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{All right. I'll come another time.}
{Speech 5}{}{This is private property, be a good fellow and move along.}
{Speech 10}{}{How can I help you?}
{Speech 10 Answer 11}{}{I'd like@sex@||| to ask a couple of questions.}
{Speech 11}{}{What questions?}
{Speech 11 Answer 12}{}{Could you tell me how to get to the library?}
{Speech 11 Answer 16}{}{Lovely weather, isn't it?}
{Speech 11 Answer 19}{}{Hey! Your whole back is white!}
{Speech 11 Answer 23}{}{Are you the one selling the antique wardrobe?}
{Speech 11 Answer Exit}{}{That's it, I've got to go, bye! [Leave]}
{Speech 12}{}{Have you lost your mind? What the hell library at three in the morning?}
{Speech 12 Answer 13}{}{But it's not three in the morning!}
{Speech 13}{}{And what difference does it make? What do you need the library for?}
{Speech 13 Answer 14}{}{I want to read a book, I just can't stand it anymore..}
{Speech 14}{}{You need the outhouse or something?}
{Speech 14 Answer 15}{}{No, I need the complete works of Brockhaus and Efron in twenty-three and a half volumes.}
{Speech 15}{}{@sex@|Buddy|Honey|, I don't get it, are you making fun of me, or are you just @sex@|an idiot|a fool|? }
{Speech 15 Answer 11}{}{Why call names right away, you'd better just answer the question...}
{Speech 16}{}{Not true. Ordinary, lousy weather.}
{Speech 16 Answer 17}{}{But the air, the air! Can you smell what a scent it is?}
{Speech 17}{}{No, I can't smell anything... Although, yeah, it stinks. When was the last time you washed@sex@||| yourself?}
{Speech 17 Answer 18}{}{Maybe working as a cop dulls your senses.}
{Speech 18}{}{Is that a jab? Who do you think you're talking to?}
{Speech 18 Answer 11}{}{No, not at all. May I ask one more question?}
{Speech 19}{}{Oh come on! [Turns his head, trying to look at his back] Everything's fine, what kind of nonsense are you talking?}
{Speech 19 Answer 20}{}{It's a joke, hee-hee-hee!}
{Speech 20}{}{Bah. And what's so funny about that joke? Your back isn't white, by the way. But it seems you stepped in a brahmin patty somewhere@sex@|||.}
{Speech 20 Answer 21}{}{What? What patty?}
{Speech 21}{}{Look at your own feet. Knee-deep in crap.}
{Speech 21 Answer 22}{}{Oh! It can't be! What a load of bull, everything's fine with me!}
{Speech 22}{}{That was a joke too, ha. Funny?}
{Speech 22 Answer 11}{}{Not very. Can I ask one more question?}
{Speech 23}{}{A wardrobe? You've got something mixed up@sex@|||, @sex@|smart guy|sweetheart|.}
{Speech 23 Answer 24}{}{Not very. Can I ask one more question?}
{Speech 24}{}{My name isn't Jack.}
{Speech 24 Answer 25}{}{And where can I find Jack?}
{Speech 25}{}{How should I know? What's this idiotic habit of pestering cops with stupid questions?}
{Speech 25 Answer 11}{}{ We didn't go to any universities, we weren't taught manners. Can I ask one more question?}
